## SOS FLOW (FULL CALL CHAIN)

FRONTEND:
DashboardScreenV2.jsx в†’ handleSOS() в†’ api.sos.trigger()
api.js в†’ POST /api/v1/sos

BACKEND:
routes/api.php в†’ Route::post('/sos', [SosController::class, 'store'])
SosController.php::store() в†’ creates SosEvent в†’ dispatches SOSTriggered
SOSTriggered.php (Event) в†’ contains user_id, location, is_duress
QueueSosAlert.php (Listener) в†’ dispatches SendSosAlertJob
SendSosAlertJob.php (Job) в†’ creates EmergencyEscalation
в†’ creates SafetyIncident
в†’ looks up TrustedContacts (by phone)
в†’ creates IncidentNotification for each contact
в†’ sends notifications

MODELS INVOLVED:
EmergencyEscalation.php
SafetyIncident.php
IncidentNotification.php
TrustedContact.php (USES 'phone')

